title: Disconnect From Discord | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Disconnect From Discord | Joel Osteen
description:
Don't let seeds of discontentment take root in your heart. If you'll stay on the high road, God will help you become everything that you were created to be.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
